item.title: Audio for "ITRC: Overview of the Tire-Derived Chemicals 6PPD & 6PPD-quinone," May 1, 2025
item.description: In October 2024, ITRC released the 6PPD & 6PPD-quinone Guidance Document to provide environmental professionals and communities with information about the current science and regulatory framework of 6PPD and 6PPD-quinone (6PPD-q). 6PPD-q is a contaminant of emerging concern and is a transformation product of the tire anti-degradant (6PPD), an antiozonant used in tires...
